        "content": "## Bootstrap issue index\n\nRun **once** after deploy (or after n8n restart \u2014 in-memory store clears).\n\nLoads 427 pre-exported issue documents from `/home/node/.n8n-files/leverage_docs.json` into the shared Simple Vector Store (`leverage_issues`). Takes ~5\u201310 min on CPU.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "73fdc563-a379-43a4-87d1-99d8bff46acf",
      "name": "About",
